description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Radiology department at St Helier Hospital and Epsom General Hospital are looking for experienced sonographers to join our pool of bank sonographers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for sonographers with obstetrics and gynecology skills as well as general abdominal, MSK or vascular skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are happy to tailor the lists around your expertise and your availability at one of our sites most convenient to you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The staffbank for Epsom and St Helier NHS Trust can offer flexible working hours particularly at the evenings and weekends as well as sessions during normal working hours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;PAYE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Days £33ph&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Evening (5pm to 8pm) £45ph&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Weekends (9am to 5pm)£50ph&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Flexible hours&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;StaffBank can offer you the flexibility you desire with the benefit of the NHS pension scheme, and more. Our jobs would bring a brilliant opportunity to anyone who is looking to top up their current salary, skills or to accommodate their personal circumstances. You’ll be reliable, dedicated and flexible, with a commitment to competent, high quality care delivery.&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;StaffBank requires you to have:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Registration with the HCPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Eligibility to work within the UK&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;StaffBank can offer you:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Flexible hours&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Free core skills training and annual updates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Support from a friendly and approachable team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Excellent, Competitive pay rates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Access to the NHS Pension&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As part of the recruitment process you will be required to complete an enhanced DBS check. We regret that we cannot accept applications from candidates seeking work permits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Apply now to find out more about this incredible opportunity! Successful candidates will also have an opportunity to learn about our great benefits!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
